Pasta with Tomato Sauce

25 min
$5
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

glutendairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariannut-free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Description

Delicious pasta coated in a rich tomato sauce, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • pasta (any shape): 8 ounces
  • tomato sauce: 2 cups
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • grated parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup
  • fresh basil leaves: 1/4 cup (optional)
